; Minimal DNS zone for the AutoTLS E2E canary.
; The p2p-forge ipparser plugin reads this at CoreDNS startup; it needs
; an SOA + NS record for the forge domain. We don't need glue records
; or A/AAAA entries: ipparser synthesises per-peer subdomains from the
; embedded IP in <peerid>.libp2p.test hostnames at query time.
$TTL 300
$ORIGIN libp2p.test.

@ 86400 IN SOA ns1.libp2p.test. admin.libp2p.test. (
    2026010101  ; serial
    86400       ; refresh
    2400        ; retry
    604800      ; expire
    86400       ; minimum
)

libp2p.test. 86400 IN NS ns1.libp2p.test.
ns1.libp2p.test. 86400 IN A 127.0.0.1
